 States presidential election in Illinois, 1984|1984]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''64.5%''' ''20,294''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|34.8% ''10,942''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.7% ''229''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1980|1980]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''53.9%''' ''16,370''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|29.4% ''8,913''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|16.7% ''5,082''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1976|1976]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''59.2%''' ''18,193''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|37.5% ''11,535''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|3.3% ''1,000''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1972|1972]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''60.3%''' ''18,910''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|39.4% ''12,375''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.3% ''99''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1968|1968]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''63.2%''' ''14,535''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|30.3% ''6,974''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|6.5% ''1,490''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1964|1964]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''53.5%''' ''11,791''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shad